<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢٩٧٩ - <span class="c4">[٨]</span> <span class="c2">(رافع بن خديج)</span> قوله: <span class="c2">(وله نفقته)</span>. . . . .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
